        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "f2589443954ee12b",
        "text": "I don't know if you're from New York or been there, but the New York Public Library used to be this reservoir. So they actually drained the reservoir and made it a library. \n"
      },
      "after": "b043a9c893b5ba7a",
      "date": 1487473317612
